news.title: NGT issues notice to Rajasthan government over pollution by brick kilns
news.para: National Green Tribunal (NGT) central zone bench Bhopal issued notice to the state government on a petition over pollution caused by brick kilns using coal. The next hearing of the case is on October 18.

news.title: Find cost of 870 trees cut for MLAs housing project: Orissa HC
news.para: The order came on a PIL filed by Cuttack-based social activist Jayanti Das against the cutting of trees for the Rs 549. 41-crore MLA Colony project in the capital.

news.title: Ludhiana builders seek Arvind Kejriwal's intervention over high construction cost
news.para: Industrialists rue that at a time, when construction industry was in need of government’s help to control input costs, it has done just the opposite by not implementing mining policy.
